headline: Violent murder of a student in Los Olivos
author: NA
content: Ricardo Bojórquez Álvarez narrated the brutal killing and dismemberment of Martín Jesús Caccire Castañeda, an economics student.

headline: Police officer José Navarro Ríos killed during confrontation
author: NA
content: José Navarro Ríos was fatally shot in the abdomen during a confrontation with suspects.

headline: Woman arrested in Ate for attempted robbery with a hidden revolver
author: NA
content: A woman was caught attempting to rob a grocery store, hiding a revolver in her bra.

headline: Detectives from Diprove arrest two suspects involved in vehicle thefts
author: NA
content: Cárdenas P Dirnic and Miguel Calderón Sara via were arrested along with stolen vehicle plates in a Hyundai car.

headline: Three suspects flee during police operation near Trapiche and Los Inkas avenues
author: NA
content: Three individuals escaped during a police operation, while others were apprehended.

headline: Fiscal Cirilo's involvement in the case
author: NA
content: Fiscal Cirilo was involved in the investigation and pursuit of suspects.

headline: Two men arrested in Carabayllo for allegedly violating minors
author: NA
content: Miguel Estaban and another man were arrested on charges of sexually abusing minors under false pretenses.
